<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/industries/2014/04/16/no-vacations-no-salary-mother-day-ad-for-american-greetings-goes-viral/">Motherâs Day ad</a> goes viral.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Placing ads on search engines <a href="//online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702304626304579505663515509926">isn&#8217;t paying off</a> for many small businesses.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Can &#8220;liking&#8221; a brand online void <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/04/17/business/when-liking-a-brand-online-voids-the-right-to-sue.html">a consumer&#8217;s right to sue</a>? <span id="more-84648"></span></p>
