<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ An âInternet of thingsâ company <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/04/16/this-internet-of-things-company-works-with-coca-cola-just-raised-50m-smart-soda-cans/">just raised</a> $50 million for smart soda cans.</p>
