<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Health Care</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The states that embraced the Affordable Care Act are seeing <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/4/16/5620020/the-uninsured-rate-is-falling-three-times-faster-in-states-that-like">a much faster decline</a> in their uninsured rate, according to a Gallup poll.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here&#8217;s how <a href="//www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/04/14/how-being-a-doctor-became-the-most-miserable-profession.html">being a doctor</a> became a miserable profession.</p>
