<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A group of Pennsylvania lawmakers <a href="//www.philly.com/philly/news/Lawmakers_propose_tax_breaks_for_small_businesses.html">offered a package</a> of legislation to help small-business owners.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Cockroaches <a href="//observer.com/2014/04/signs-of-life-pest-problems-plague-sohos-chicest-food-spots/">rain from the ceiling</a> at a New York sushi restaurant.</p>
