<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Rising <a href="//online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303626804579505823396915820?">costs erode</a> Google profits, but the company announces a <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/04/16/google-launches-chrome-remote-desktop-on-android-allowing-mobile-access-to-your-pc/">new application</a> that allows mobile access to your PC and is working on a <a href="//www.policymic.com/articles/87795/google-patented-a-new-device-that-could-give-you-superhuman-sight">new device</a> âstraight out of &#8216;Star Trek.&#8217;â</p>
